2026-05-18T00:14:05.3582808Z [36;1m        print(failures$result)[0m
2026-05-18T00:14:05.3583273Z [36;1m        testthat::snapshot_accept()[0m
2026-05-18T00:14:05.3583936Z [36;1m        writeLines("changed=true", Sys.getenv("GITHUB_OUTPUT"))[0m
2026-05-18T00:14:05.3584507Z [36;1m      } else {[0m
